channel.title: Printer Settings :: CID guide website
channel.description: Once you are satified with the object placement, move to the right menu. Print settings Here you will see a list of settings for layer heights: 0.1 mm will be the most precise setting, good for visual detail or mechanical functionality. 0.15 mm has both SPEED and STRUCTURAL options, choose SPEED for a faster print, or STRUCTURAL for a sturdier print.
